      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Turns out, these things won’t make nearly as much of a dent in reducing our collective carbon footprint than we’d like to believe. Far less than changing even 1% of the hundreds of things that will happen today that you have absolutely no control over.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The thousands of commercial planes that will fly by every hour.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The hundreds of thousands of gas-guzzling cars that drive around every minute.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The millions of businesses that will keep their lights on—every second of every day and night—with no end in sight.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Doing your part likely won’t change a thing. But that doesn’t mean it’s not worth doing. And it especially doesn’t mean you should stop.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It simply means that we’d do better to let go of the",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "exhausting belief",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "that we can stop this. That we have to. That we must. And get on to",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "doing what matters",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ".",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://jonleighton.name/2020/the-other-crisis/"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Not by focusing on what we can’t change.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "By by leveraging",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "all",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "that we can.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
